articles.title: Australian river filled with millions of dead fish as residents complain of ‘putrid’ smell - Fox News
articles.description: Thousands of fish around the Australian Outback town of Menindee have washed up in recent weeks, clogging a major river, and scientists believe depleted oxygen levels are to blame.
articles.content:
